==English==
===Etymology===
Contraction of ‘God's hooks’, with reference to the nails of the crucifixion.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/gædˈzu:ks/}}

===Interjection===
'''gadzooks'''

# (''archaic'') An expression of surprise, shock etc.

